              >
                What is the most watched Ted Talk?
              </h3>
              <span
                class="text-[#EB0028] text-xl font-light ml-4 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform"
                >+</span
              >
            </summary>
            <div
              class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"
              itemscope
              itemprop="acceptedAnswer"
              itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"
            >
              <p itemprop="text">
                The most watched TED talk is "Do schools kill creativity?" by
                education expert Sir Ken Robinson. First delivered at the
                TED2006 conference, this talk has accumulated more than 75
                million combined views across official platforms, remaining the
                ultimate fan-favorite.
              </p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details
            class="group py-6"
            itemscope
            itemprop="mainEntity"
            itemtype="https://schema.org/Question"
          >
            <summary
              class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none"
            >
              <h3
                class="text-base font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-black group-open:text-[#EB0028] transition-colors"
                itemprop="name"
              >
                Do TED talkers get paid?
              </h3>
              <span
                class="text-[#EB0028] text-xl font-light ml-4 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform"
                >+</span
              >
            </summary>
            <div
              class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"
              itemscope
              itemprop="acceptedAnswer"
              itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"
            >
              <p itemprop="text">
                No, speakers at official TED conferences do not get paid a
                speaker fee. However, TED covers their travel costs,
                accommodation, and provides tickets to the multi-day conference.
                Speakers benefit from massive global exposure, professional
                speaker coaching, and the prestige associated with giving a TED
                talk. Most TEDx events operate similarly and do not pay
                speakers.
              </p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details
            class="group py-6"
            itemscope
            itemprop="mainEntity"
            itemtype="https://schema.org/Question"
          >
            <summary
              class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none"
            >
              <h3
                class="text-base font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-black group-open:text-[#EB0028] transition-colors"
                itemprop="name"
              >
                What is the most inspiring Ted talk?
              </h3>
              <span
