              itemscope
              itemprop="acceptedAnswer"
              itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"
            >
              <p itemprop="text">
                In TED talks, TED stands for Technology, Entertainment, and
                Design. The organization started in 1984 as a conference where
                these three fields converged. Since then, the topics have
                broadened to include almost every discipline imaginable.
              </p>
            </div>
